WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:11.060 --> 00:00:12.060
So, you've been waiting for me?

00:00:13.110 --> 00:00:14.900
Have you waited so long to play with me?

00:00:17.580 --> 00:00:19.110
Ouch! That hurts!

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:22.430
The sounds “Chikey chikey” are all made 
by Hyouta when he is excited.

00:00:23.700 --> 00:00:25.320
Though he never bite my fingers with all his might, 

00:00:26.070 --> 00:00:28.240
his sharp and long front teeth hurt me 
when he's excited in this way.

00:00:29.500 --> 00:00:31.640
Soon, he will stamp the ground mumbling 
his complaints to insist on more playing.

00:00:37.490 --> 00:00:40.030
He looks unsatisfied stamping 
his feet in frustration, doesn't he?

00:00:46.990 --> 00:00:47.650
Do you want to play with me?

00:00:48.370 --> 00:00:49.830
Are you enjoying this play?

00:00:50.870 --> 00:00:51.960
Ouch! That hurts!

00:00:52.880 --> 00:00:55.160
Your teeth are sharp, so they hurt me.

00:01:03.230 --> 00:01:05.030
You are really grumbling.

00:01:11.210 --> 00:01:13.290
Are you mad at me for not playing enough with you?

00:01:18.240 --> 00:01:19.460
Are you enjoying this play?

00:01:30.330 --> 00:01:32.010
Ouch...

00:01:49.150 --> 00:01:51.080
OK, I'll let you chew my fingers, as you like.

00:01:56.640 --> 00:01:59.080
This glove is long enough to guard my wrist.

00:01:59.910 --> 00:02:02.740
Besides, it's double layered.

00:02:04.850 --> 00:02:07.610
OK, chew, chew!

00:02:16.630 --> 00:02:18.840
What a rodent!

00:02:20.150 --> 00:02:22.440
Every communication is done with teeth!

00:02:32.100 --> 00:02:33.190
Spring (Amorous season) has come!

